gw.api.json.mapping

Interface JsonMappingProperty


  • public interface JsonMappingProperty
    A mapper for a single JSON Schema property. A JsonMappingProperty takes the mapper's root object as its input and produces a value for the associated JSON Schema property as its output.

      • evaluatePredicate

        boolean evaluatePredicate(@NotNull
                          @NotNull ISymbolTable symbolTable)
        Evaluates the predicate expression, if any, given the runtime ISymbolTable that contains the root object for the mapper. If no predicate expression has been defined, this will return true.
        Parameters:
        symbolTable - the symbol table to use for evaluation
        Returns:
        the result of evaluating the predicate expression, or true if no predicate expression has been defined

      • evaluatePropertyKey

        @Nullable
@Nullable java.lang.String evaluatePropertyKey(@NotNull
                                                         @NotNull ISymbolTable symbolTable,
                                                         @NotNull
                                                         @NotNull java.lang.Object value)
        Evaluates the propertyKey expression, if any, given the runtime ISymbolTable that contains the root object for the mapper and the object to determine a key for. If no key expression has been defined, this will return null.
        Parameters:
        symbolTable - the symbol table to use for evaluation
        value - the element whose key should be evaluated
        Returns:
        the result of evaluating the key expression for the given value

      • evaluatePropertyValue

        @Nullable
@Nullable java.lang.Object evaluatePropertyValue(@NotNull
                                                           @NotNull ISymbolTable symbolTable,
                                                           @NotNull
                                                           @NotNull java.lang.Object value)
        Evaluates the propertyValue expression, if any, given the runtime ISymbolTable that contains the root object for the mapper and the object to determine a key for. If no propertyValue expression has been defined, this will return back the value object that was originally passed in.
        Parameters:
        symbolTable - the symbol table to use for evaluation
        value - the element whose property value should be evaluated
        Returns:
        the result of evaluating the propertyValue expression for the given value, or the value itself if no such expression has been defined
